    "name": "Aim Assault",
    "steam_appid": 3047310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/3db6febf05297884312c57fae7274732.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1252 height=174 /></span><strong>Aim Assault</strong> <strong>brings the thrill of old-school arcade rail-shooters into the world of virtual reality. Blast through various enemies, master different gunplay styles, and race the timer to climb to the top of the global leaderboards.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight different types of enemies and boss fights in intense situations and ever-changing, rich environments. Dodge barrages of bullets, take down the bad guys, and save the world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/4acf30d278474b4988f08f837cfd1127.poster.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/4acf30d278474b4988f08f837cfd1127.webm?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/4acf30d278474b4988f08f837cfd1127.mp4?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/15ce61850be1128242a5ee19cbfdabc3.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1560 height=157 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The full game introduces several campaign levels with different modes and extra challenges to play through. You will fight in various environments, saving the president from a hijacked airplane or chasing a military helicopter across rooftops during a bank robbery heist. Rescue a hostage in an exotic villa or face the legendary war pilot on top of a skyscraper.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/e983f13841c1c638d0c7f5a8b63bfe9f.poster.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/e983f13841c1c638d0c7f5a8b63bfe9f.webm?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/e983f13841c1c638d0c7f5a8b63bfe9f.mp4?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock a wide selection of weapons, each with unique skins and special effects.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Enemies won’t be your only challenge. You can test your skills in different aim challenges and modes available for each level. For less-experienced players, an Easy mode is available; for those seeking a tougher experience, each level includes a One-Life difficulty or even an Insta-Death mode.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/66b73daed64105285d1364759cab97b1.poster.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/66b73daed64105285d1364759cab97b1.webm?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/66b73daed64105285d1364759cab97b1.mp4?t=1763736948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Think you have the best and fastest aim? We’ve set up a global leaderboard to find out who the best arcade shooter in the world truly is. Each difficulty setting and gun loadout has its own leaderboard. Collect points across individual leaderboards to become the global number one. Don’t forget to share your best score with us on our Discord!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the world of Aim Assault!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047310/extras/3db6febf05297884312c57fae7274732.avif?t=1763736948\" width=1252 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional information: If your game crashes when using Steam Link with Steam XR runtime, enable the “Meta Plugin Compatibility” option in SteamVR’s OpenXR settings.</p>",
